{
  "title": "Garlicky Molten Russian Garlic Borscht",
  "description": "A hearty Russian-inspired borscht dish enhanced by the pungency of garlic and a burst of citrus, great for post-workout restoration. Featuring unwaxed lime and a low-sodium broth.",
  "cuisine": "Russian",
